Create New Record
	Client  Side
		- Validations for add (for empty, date/email format)
		- Prepare parameter list
		- Pass ajax request

	Server Side
		- Capture Params
		- Validate (for empty, date/email format, field lengths)

		-> IF valid
			- Save data
			- Display OK message
			- Reload datagrid
			- Clear and reset form
		-> ELSE invalid
			- Keep entered values in fields
			- Display the error message
			- Highlignt the field with errorneous data











